WEBVTT

01:27.470 --> 01:31.940
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.190 --> 01:34.890
[Episode 12]

01:49.200 --> 01:54.120
[The Cutest One in the World]

01:50.229 --> 01:51.680
I know you're angry.

01:52.310 --> 01:54.440
But can you give me a chance to explain?

01:56.590 --> 01:57.430
I'm sorry.

01:58.509 --> 01:59.310
In the future,

01:59.740 --> 02:02.930
[The Cutest One in the World]

01:59.950 --> 02:01.350
will I still have the chance to treat you

02:01.350 --> 02:03.010
to the loving lunch made by me?

02:21.520 --> 02:22.960
What terrible cooking?

02:23.630 --> 02:24.750
The egg is even burnt.

02:24.120 --> 02:29.370
[Lihai Meteorology]

02:39.470 --> 02:41.270
-Be careful on the way.
-Bye bye.

02:44.680 --> 02:45.810
What are you doing here?

02:45.810 --> 02:47.150
I brought you some fruit salad.

02:47.150 --> 02:48.010
I don't want it.

02:48.560 --> 02:49.430
There are many raisins in it.

02:49.430 --> 02:50.290
I don't want it.

02:52.820 --> 02:55.140
Have you seen that news recently?

02:56.150 --> 02:58.440
The PUA Class? Undercover agents, right?

02:58.440 --> 02:59.470
I saw the news.

02:59.930 --> 03:01.710
The informant inside there was you, right?

03:01.710 --> 03:02.290
Yes.

03:02.800 --> 03:05.840
So the person Chen Xue saw that day
was you.

03:05.910 --> 03:06.840
You were afraid of being exposed,

03:06.840 --> 03:08.960
so you colluded with Yan Ling
to lie to me.

03:08.960 --> 03:10.240
Yes, I was lying to you.

03:10.240 --> 03:11.240
You even said yes?

03:12.000 --> 03:12.680
No, no, no.

03:12.680 --> 03:13.140
But I...

03:13.590 --> 03:15.280
But I really didn't mean that
when I said it.

03:15.280 --> 03:16.280
What did you mean?

03:17.800 --> 03:19.860
I'd like to see how you'll explain it.

03:21.150 --> 03:21.680
Well...

03:24.560 --> 03:25.680
Don't be angry.

03:27.400 --> 03:28.200
Look.

03:28.870 --> 03:31.100
That news was so unclear,

03:31.120 --> 03:32.980
but you could still recognize me.

03:33.480 --> 03:36.000
It means you still care about me.

03:36.320 --> 03:37.650
How can you be like this?

03:38.640 --> 03:39.079
So...

03:39.079 --> 03:40.740
You think it's over like this?

03:41.310 --> 03:42.710
That was clearly a heroic act.

03:42.710 --> 03:44.570
Why couldn't you just tell me?

03:45.120 --> 03:45.710
Well...

03:45.710 --> 03:46.400
I know.

03:46.960 --> 03:48.520
You were afraid
I'd mess things up for you.

03:48.520 --> 03:49.020
No!

03:49.120 --> 03:50.840
Or were you afraid I'd stop you?

03:50.840 --> 03:52.280
That thing was too dangerous.

03:52.280 --> 03:53.079
If I had told you,

03:53.079 --> 03:54.520
wouldn't you worry about me?

03:54.520 --> 03:55.520
Also, um...

03:56.360 --> 03:59.180
In order to infiltrate the enemy,

03:59.520 --> 04:01.840
I had to do some bad things,

04:01.840 --> 04:03.570
which were even a little dirty.

04:04.310 --> 04:04.860
Look.

04:05.430 --> 04:06.490
You are so innocent

04:06.910 --> 04:08.000
and quite naive.

04:08.680 --> 04:09.680
I was afraid...

04:11.680 --> 04:13.710
So you and Yan Ling are adults,

04:14.280 --> 04:16.680
comrades-in-arms and undercover heroes.

04:17.630 --> 04:18.070
No.

04:18.070 --> 04:19.070
I'm almost 30.

04:19.160 --> 04:20.480
And you're still saying that I'm naive.

04:20.480 --> 04:22.190
You might as well just call me stupid.

04:22.190 --> 04:22.820
No, no, no.

04:23.040 --> 04:24.070
I didn't mean that.

04:24.070 --> 04:24.800
Let go.

04:26.160 --> 04:26.870
Let go!

04:34.070 --> 04:36.130
What will we have for dinner tonight?

04:36.190 --> 04:38.120
We haven't even had breakfast yet,

04:38.150 --> 04:39.920
and you're already thinking about dinner.

04:39.920 --> 04:40.980
It's too hot today.

04:41.510 --> 04:43.110
Let's eat cold rice noodles.

04:46.630 --> 04:48.630
Why do you suddenly want to eat this?

04:49.159 --> 04:50.830
Dr. Luo asked us

04:50.830 --> 04:52.830
whether we liked cold rice noodles.

04:53.830 --> 04:55.090
Dr. Luo came to see you?

04:57.070 --> 04:57.560
No.

04:58.270 --> 05:00.400
He hasn't come to see me for a long time.

05:02.830 --> 05:04.430
I just want to ask about this.

05:05.800 --> 05:07.850
Will I still have a chance to eat

05:07.950 --> 05:10.550
the Sweet and Sour Ribs
made by Uncle Luo Liang?

05:11.720 --> 05:13.160
His cooking tastes just the same

05:13.160 --> 05:14.090
as Godmother's.

05:26.680 --> 05:27.630
[The problem has been solved.
I'll wash the outfit and return it to you.]

05:27.660 --> 05:28.300
[Okay. No hurry.]

05:28.330 --> 05:29.030
[Thank you for today.]

05:29.140 --> 05:33.040
[Dr. Luo Liang]

05:39.090 --> 05:41.560
[Dr. Luo Liang]

05:41.600 --> 05:41.690
[3 days ago]

05:41.690 --> 05:42.520
[Thank you for trusting me
and telling me your story.]

05:42.550 --> 05:43.990
[Rest early.]

05:48.950 --> 05:50.390
Can we talk again?

05:51.159 --> 05:53.159
It's really not like what you think.

05:53.240 --> 05:54.220
It's because...

05:58.820 --> 06:04.180
[Typing...]

06:08.610 --> 06:09.780
[Can we talk again?]

06:09.810 --> 06:11.210
[It's really not like what you think.
It's because...]

06:27.170 --> 06:30.780
[Typing...]

06:42.610 --> 06:45.100
[Dongchuan Public Security Department]

06:45.170 --> 06:47.390
[Interrogation Room 1]

06:50.490 --> 06:52.730
[Interrogation Room 1]

07:02.240 --> 07:02.970
You can do it.

07:22.380 --> 07:23.570
[Interrogator] [Scribe]

07:27.480 --> 07:28.680
I'm warning you guys!

07:29.390 --> 07:30.590
I'm a Pazion citizen.

07:30.870 --> 07:33.800
I demand that you should notify
the Pazion Consulate immediately.

07:33.800 --> 07:34.800
If the people from the consulate
don't come,

07:34.800 --> 07:36.190
I won't say a word.

07:40.680 --> 07:42.430
According to Article 6 of the Criminal Law

07:42.430 --> 07:44.240
of the People's Republic of China,

07:44.240 --> 07:45.190
foreigners who commit crimes

07:45.190 --> 07:47.600
within Chinese territory
are subject to this law,

07:47.600 --> 07:50.090
except as otherwise

07:50.630 --> 07:52.360
specifically provided by law.

07:54.560 --> 07:56.720
Do you think you're special enough?

08:09.040 --> 08:10.700
What do you want me to call you?

08:11.000 --> 08:11.480
Xia Yi,

08:12.630 --> 08:13.800
Pongsri Leekpa,

08:14.430 --> 08:15.160
or...

08:15.750 --> 08:16.630
Lin Huosheng?

08:18.240 --> 08:21.800
Lin Huosheng is the name
on the Chinese household register.

08:22.070 --> 08:23.120
Pongsri Leekpa

08:23.120 --> 08:25.610
is the name in Pazion
after the plastic surgery.

08:25.610 --> 08:26.780
Xia Yi

08:27.020 --> 08:29.420
is the alias for fraud
in the outside world.

08:29.950 --> 08:30.390
Right?

08:30.850 --> 08:32.980
[Interrogator]

08:35.669 --> 08:36.669
Bank statements.

08:41.960 --> 08:44.120
We've obtained
Jian Leilei's bank statements

08:43.490 --> 08:44.680
[Lihai Commercial Bank
Account Historical Transaction Statement]

08:44.750 --> 08:46.000
The records show that

08:46.670 --> 08:47.960
the first 500,000 yuan

08:47.960 --> 08:50.490
she had transferred
out of a client's account

08:50.790 --> 08:52.950
was withdrawn in cash at the counter.

08:53.240 --> 08:54.430
A day later,

08:54.600 --> 08:56.420
[Lihai Commercial Bank
Account Historical Transaction Statement]

08:55.360 --> 08:57.390
your bank account
in the name of Lin Huosheng

08:57.390 --> 09:00.030
just received a 500,000 cash deposit.

09:05.320 --> 09:06.390
You've really mastered

09:06.390 --> 09:09.030
this trick and used it so well.

09:09.770 --> 09:11.230
While dating Jian Leilei,

09:11.910 --> 09:13.910
you gave her fake luxury goods
as gifts first

09:13.910 --> 09:15.840
and then asked her to lend you cash.

09:16.870 --> 09:18.630
Usually, girls in this situation

09:18.630 --> 09:20.480
find it hard to refuse you, right?

09:20.480 --> 09:21.320
After that,

09:21.630 --> 09:24.030
via small transfers,

09:24.080 --> 09:26.030
you returned a little money to her
in installments

09:26.030 --> 09:26.830
to build trust

09:27.270 --> 09:28.960
and pave the way for a bigger loan later.

09:28.960 --> 09:31.600
Meanwhile,
it could also leave transfer records,

09:31.600 --> 09:33.080
making it look like

09:33.360 --> 09:35.220
she was borrowing money from you.

09:38.030 --> 09:38.720
Am I right?

09:40.630 --> 09:41.960
She did it voluntarily.

09:42.840 --> 09:44.370
I couldn't help it, either.

09:44.910 --> 09:48.970
That's because she fell in love with me
after sleeping with me a few times.

10:00.360 --> 10:01.160
Do you like it?

10:01.200 --> 10:02.090
Yes, I do.

10:12.240 --> 10:13.600
Will you marry me?

10:13.600 --> 10:14.890
Yes, I will.

10:15.150 --> 10:16.810
Thank you for saying yes to me.

10:23.210 --> 10:24.750
I didn't expect that

10:26.510 --> 10:28.110
you would distrust me so much

10:28.480 --> 10:30.340
when we were about to get married.

10:34.160 --> 10:36.550
Honey, of course I trust you.

10:36.550 --> 10:38.390
Otherwise,
I wouldn't have mortgaged the house

10:38.390 --> 10:39.690
to support you.

10:39.910 --> 10:42.910
But your investment
really keeps losing money.

10:43.630 --> 10:44.950
If you need projects,

10:45.150 --> 10:47.210
I still have a few clients at the bank.

10:48.120 --> 10:49.980
Don't mention your clients to me.

10:51.440 --> 10:52.240
As you got those clients

10:52.240 --> 10:53.630
by flirting and smiling,

10:53.630 --> 10:54.910
can they even be considered as clients?

10:54.910 --> 10:56.200
How could you think of me like that?

10:56.200 --> 10:58.030
You forced me to think like that.

11:01.240 --> 11:01.840
Let me tell you,

11:01.840 --> 11:02.570
Jian Leilei.

11:03.480 --> 11:05.030
Don't think that working at the bank

11:05.030 --> 11:06.270
gives you the right to

11:06.270 --> 11:07.730
meddle in my investments.

11:07.790 --> 11:08.910
I've handled more money

11:08.910 --> 11:10.840
than you could see in your lifetime!

11:10.840 --> 11:11.910
Honey, you've misunderstood.

11:11.910 --> 11:13.750
I really didn't mean that.

11:13.750 --> 11:15.600
I really don't think that way.

11:16.360 --> 11:17.560
Then what do you mean?

11:18.080 --> 11:19.410
You just look down on me, don't you?

11:19.410 --> 11:20.750
No, I don't.

11:20.840 --> 11:22.460
Why am I working so hard?

11:22.750 --> 11:23.240
Because I just want to

11:23.240 --> 11:24.480
prove to my parents

11:24.480 --> 11:25.120
that without them,

11:25.120 --> 11:26.380
I can still make money,

11:27.270 --> 11:27.670
and without them,

11:27.670 --> 11:29.720
I can also marry the woman I love.

11:30.720 --> 11:31.270
Only in this way

11:31.270 --> 11:32.430
can I avoid seeing

11:32.430 --> 11:33.270
those rich girls they've picked out,

11:33.270 --> 11:35.500
whose families match mine in status.

11:36.000 --> 11:36.930
Do you know that?

11:37.200 --> 11:37.860
Yes, I know.

11:39.480 --> 11:40.820
But I didn't expect that

11:41.440 --> 11:43.970
just like them,
you would also disbelieve me.

11:47.390 --> 11:49.790
Honey, I really didn't mean that.

11:49.790 --> 11:50.870
I'm sorry.

11:51.200 --> 11:53.000
What's wrong? Let me take a look.

11:54.510 --> 11:56.370
How did you get injured like this?

11:56.720 --> 11:57.450
Does it hurt?

12:01.510 --> 12:02.440
In your opinion,

12:03.910 --> 12:05.570
if I hadn't been so desperate,

12:06.870 --> 12:08.530
would I borrow money from you?

12:11.310 --> 12:12.970
Did you borrow money outside?

12:17.200 --> 12:19.240
They say marriage is a gamble.

12:21.390 --> 12:22.720
I've bet everything I have

12:22.720 --> 12:25.070
and might even need to bet my life soon.

12:25.440 --> 12:26.120
But what about you,

12:26.120 --> 12:26.850
Jian Leilei?

12:27.840 --> 12:29.840
What have you done for our family?

12:32.870 --> 12:33.600
Don't worry.

12:35.200 --> 12:36.930
I will never drag you into this.

12:39.000 --> 12:39.670
Honey!

12:39.670 --> 12:41.630
Don't leave. Honey!

12:41.630 --> 12:43.290
Don't leave! I'm begging you!

12:43.390 --> 12:45.120
I'll definitely find a solution.

12:45.120 --> 12:48.240
Don't leave.
I'll definitely find a solution.

12:52.630 --> 12:54.560
You have no idea how much I love you.

13:22.440 --> 13:23.240
Besides,

13:24.200 --> 13:27.260
I also didn't force her
to embezzle her clients' money.

13:27.320 --> 13:29.120
I really didn't know about this.

13:29.840 --> 13:31.240
She's a mid‑level employee at the bank,

13:31.240 --> 13:32.570
and at this age,

13:33.240 --> 13:35.840
logically speaking,
she should be quite rich.

13:36.000 --> 13:38.330
Unexpectedly, she had so little savings.

13:39.270 --> 13:41.120
So in order to cheat more money

13:41.120 --> 13:42.600
out of Jian Leilei,

13:44.240 --> 13:45.150
you sent her

13:45.150 --> 13:47.350
the intimate videos you had taken of her

13:47.550 --> 13:49.910
and kept blackmailing and threatening her,

13:49.910 --> 13:52.030
saying that you'd expose the videos
if she didn't pay,

13:52.030 --> 13:54.290
until you finally drove her to her death.

13:57.670 --> 13:59.800
After Jian Leilei committed suicide,

13:59.910 --> 14:01.960
I was planning to just leave.

14:02.320 --> 14:04.550
But I listened to Yu Kexin,
that wretched woman,

14:04.550 --> 14:06.010
and played along with her.

14:06.120 --> 14:08.720
Otherwise,
you wouldn't have been able to find me.

14:08.720 --> 14:10.600
Don't retreat.
They're already targetting you.

14:10.600 --> 14:11.150
Just fight back first.

14:11.150 --> 14:12.410
I'm not fighting back.

14:12.600 --> 14:13.800
I need to run away now.

14:13.960 --> 14:14.440
If you run away,

14:14.440 --> 14:16.170
I'll just get trapped, won't I?

14:17.740 --> 14:18.920
What did I say?

14:19.150 --> 14:20.880
If we don't run away, we'll die.

14:23.650 --> 14:25.580
We're doomed this time, aren't we?

14:25.840 --> 14:26.820
What a coward.

14:27.080 --> 14:28.360
You're exactly the same as before.

14:28.360 --> 14:30.000
When things go wrong,
you tend to just run away.

14:30.000 --> 14:31.390
You haven't improved at all.

14:31.390 --> 14:32.390
That woman surnamed Yan

14:32.390 --> 14:33.870
tracked me down through the tattoo.

14:33.870 --> 14:34.790
If you don't fight back,

14:34.790 --> 14:36.120
we're both going to die.

14:45.230 --> 14:45.350
[Lihai Commercial Bank
Account Historical Transaction Statement]

14:45.440 --> 14:45.800
[Wanderer's Exclusive Love Course]

14:46.360 --> 14:47.270
Are you very proud of

14:47.270 --> 14:48.120
this contemptible

14:48.120 --> 14:49.960
PUA Theory you've invented?

14:50.270 --> 14:51.670
The entire telecom fraud group

14:51.670 --> 14:53.790
was established
on the basis of your theory.

14:53.790 --> 14:54.650
Let me tell you!

14:55.200 --> 14:57.320
The amount of money
involved in this case is huge.

14:57.320 --> 14:58.440
It has a bad influence,

14:58.440 --> 14:59.670
and the approaches are cruel.

14:59.670 --> 15:02.470
As the main culprit,
you'll be sentenced to death.

15:03.550 --> 15:05.200
No! I'm not the main culprit.

15:06.000 --> 15:07.400
I'm not the main culprit!

15:07.600 --> 15:09.030
I just took someone else's stuff

15:09.030 --> 15:10.510
and then gave it to Master Bei.

15:10.510 --> 15:11.670
Keep pressuring him.

15:11.670 --> 15:13.400
Confess everything honestly!

15:13.790 --> 15:15.200
Ouyang Kun
has already confessed it.

15:15.200 --> 15:17.690
All the PUA materials
were provided by you.

15:17.960 --> 15:19.000
Every word

15:19.000 --> 15:20.240
and every punctuation mark

15:19.540 --> 15:20.250
[Wanderer's Exclusive Love Course]

15:20.360 --> 15:22.080
were provided by you, Lin Huosheng.

15:22.080 --> 15:22.990
It wasn't me!

15:23.720 --> 15:24.540
I'm just a...

15:24.750 --> 15:26.240
On a website called Amusement Park,

15:26.240 --> 15:27.200
I saw someone named...

15:27.200 --> 15:28.580
named Mister share it.

15:29.200 --> 15:29.600
What?

15:30.150 --> 15:30.910
Mister!

15:34.390 --> 15:35.920
Stay calm. Don't look at me.

15:37.150 --> 15:37.880
Keep asking.

15:38.480 --> 15:39.340
Check about it.

15:42.520 --> 15:43.010
Go on.

15:45.150 --> 15:46.550
His avatar was a certain

15:46.890 --> 15:48.310
Greek monster.

15:49.390 --> 15:49.910
Yes, yes, yes.

15:49.910 --> 15:51.370
It... It's called Medusa.

15:51.440 --> 15:52.440
Then I also imitated him

15:52.440 --> 15:53.900
and made a similar avatar.

15:54.120 --> 15:54.910
But I was afraid people would say

15:54.910 --> 15:56.200
my avatar lacked originality,

15:56.200 --> 15:58.150
so I... I just changed the snake
on his avatar

15:58.150 --> 15:59.000
into a...

15:59.670 --> 16:01.910
b-b-b-big octopus.

16:02.840 --> 16:04.370
We didn't find the webpage.

16:07.270 --> 16:09.870
You think by randomly making up
an inaccessible website

16:09.870 --> 16:11.980
and inventing a fictional character,
you can find a scapegoat?

16:11.980 --> 16:13.040
I didn't make it up!

16:13.080 --> 16:13.880
It does exist!

16:13.930 --> 16:14.910
That website does exist!

16:14.910 --> 16:16.230
Originally, that website was very popular.

16:16.230 --> 16:18.120
Many people said they wanted to
become this Mister's apprentice.

16:18.120 --> 16:19.200
But later, for an unknown reason,

16:19.200 --> 16:20.790
this Mister suddenly disappeared.

16:20.790 --> 16:23.190
Then the forum and the website
were closed.

16:24.000 --> 16:25.150
Many people wondered
whether something wrong

16:25.150 --> 16:26.750
had happened to this Mister.

16:28.960 --> 16:29.960
That's almost it.

16:30.440 --> 16:31.120
How.. How...

16:31.120 --> 16:32.780
How come it can't be found now?

16:36.670 --> 16:37.840
Well, bro...

16:37.840 --> 16:38.270
Let me tell you.

16:38.270 --> 16:39.150
Everything I said is true.

16:39.150 --> 16:39.790
Turst me.

16:39.790 --> 16:40.200
Okay?

16:41.790 --> 16:42.790
Don't go!

16:43.600 --> 16:44.390
Really. Well...

16:44.390 --> 16:44.870
Let me tell you.

16:44.870 --> 16:46.870
I have screenshots
of that website.

16:48.030 --> 16:50.320
You can take a look yourselves. Really.

16:54.600 --> 16:55.720
Goodbye, Ms. Yan.

16:55.720 --> 16:56.510
Goodbye.

17:09.540 --> 17:14.160
[4 days ago]

17:17.950 --> 17:18.530
[Dr. Luo Liang]

17:18.550 --> 17:19.770
[Video Call] [Voice call]

17:19.800 --> 17:23.630
[Dr. Luo Liang]

17:43.130 --> 17:44.540
[Call History]

17:44.560 --> 17:45.530
[Calling]

17:48.220 --> 17:51.640
Hello, this is the Psychiatry Department
of Renxin Municipal Hospital.

17:51.640 --> 17:52.270
Hello.

17:52.350 --> 17:54.210
Is Dr. Luo Liang there?

17:54.790 --> 17:55.720
He has gone to Gangdao.

17:55.720 --> 17:57.180
He just left this morning.

17:58.750 --> 17:59.880
Okay. Thank you.

18:09.220 --> 18:11.460
Shan is usually quite well-behaved.

18:11.650 --> 18:13.390
I don't know why she suddenly

18:13.510 --> 18:16.750
got into a fight with the newcomer, Xu,
yesterday morning.

18:16.750 --> 18:18.160
She looks so small,

18:18.750 --> 18:20.440
but her strength is incredibly big.

18:20.440 --> 18:22.400
She smashed a pen holder on Xu's head

18:22.400 --> 18:23.460
and made him bleed.

18:24.640 --> 18:25.580
If that's the case,

18:25.580 --> 18:28.110
shouldn't they be separated
from each other?

18:29.080 --> 18:30.790
There's something you don't know.

18:30.790 --> 18:32.910
Since our hospital was acquired,

18:34.340 --> 18:37.740
the new top executives
have got some new treatment concepts.

18:38.350 --> 18:42.510
They plan to re-evaluate all patients

18:42.680 --> 18:45.740
and then decide
what treatment methods should be used.

18:49.400 --> 18:50.130
Give it to me.

18:50.830 --> 18:51.550
Give it to me.

18:51.550 --> 18:52.610
They are fighting.

18:54.200 --> 18:56.400
Xu, don't snatch other people's stuff!

18:57.580 --> 18:59.060
Stop it!

18:59.270 --> 19:00.010
Enough!

19:00.110 --> 19:01.350
Give it back to her now.

19:01.350 --> 19:02.000
Xu!

19:02.160 --> 19:04.370
It's okay. Calm down. It's okay.

19:05.310 --> 19:06.030
Let go!

19:06.030 --> 19:06.790
Xu!

19:07.000 --> 19:07.640
Xu!

19:07.640 --> 19:08.640
Did you hear that?

19:10.110 --> 19:10.510
Hey!

19:10.550 --> 19:11.240
Be careful!

19:14.440 --> 19:15.070
Xu!

19:17.510 --> 19:18.360
Be careful!

19:23.160 --> 19:23.880
Shan.

19:24.960 --> 19:26.360
What are you looking for?

19:33.920 --> 19:34.310
Shan.

19:36.030 --> 19:37.430
What are you looking for?

19:38.570 --> 19:40.160
Did you lose something?

19:41.400 --> 19:43.400
Did Xu take away something of yours?

19:44.740 --> 19:45.400
Where is it?

19:46.590 --> 19:47.790
I'll help you find it.

19:48.750 --> 19:49.240
Shan.

19:53.750 --> 19:54.510
Mom.

20:21.950 --> 20:22.600
It's okay.

20:22.850 --> 20:23.550
It's okay.

20:24.750 --> 20:25.680
Don't be afraid.

20:27.070 --> 20:28.600
You don't need to be afraid.

20:28.770 --> 20:29.700
Don't be afraid.

20:29.730 --> 20:30.490
It's okay.

20:30.790 --> 20:31.350
I'm here.

20:32.470 --> 20:33.030
I'm here.

20:34.010 --> 20:38.190
[Da Chi Ki]

20:43.960 --> 20:45.000
I have AIDS.

20:45.030 --> 20:46.960
Aren't you afraid I'll infect you?

20:47.110 --> 20:48.570
Sit over there. I'm sorry.

20:53.790 --> 20:54.600
How many people?

20:54.600 --> 20:55.080
I'm looking for someone.

20:55.080 --> 20:55.940
Suit yourself.

21:05.600 --> 21:07.290
Shan is not in a good state.

21:09.370 --> 21:10.960
So what?

21:14.820 --> 21:16.880
They said she had violent tendencies

21:17.160 --> 21:18.820
and injured another patient.

21:21.120 --> 21:23.720
I want to get her discharged
from the hospital.

21:24.290 --> 21:25.960
I know you can't take care of her,

21:25.960 --> 21:27.820
so I want to take her to Shenchuan.

21:27.890 --> 21:29.890
There's a newly-opened sanatorium there.

21:29.890 --> 21:32.220
It's spacious and has better conditions.

21:36.310 --> 21:38.910
I don't even know
how many more years I can live.

21:39.060 --> 21:40.520
When I married her mom,

21:40.720 --> 21:43.250
I just wanted to find a woman
to take care of me.

21:43.440 --> 21:44.160
By now,

21:44.650 --> 21:46.750
I can't even die
comfortably and peacefully

21:46.750 --> 21:47.810
even if I'd love to.

21:48.400 --> 21:50.130
If I take her back to Shenchuan,

21:50.710 --> 21:52.770
then you won't have to look after her.

21:58.390 --> 22:00.270
[Guardianship Authorization Letter]

22:04.890 --> 22:05.460
[Yan Ling]

22:05.550 --> 22:07.550
I just found out you went to Gangdao.

22:07.550 --> 22:08.740
When you come back,

22:08.830 --> 22:11.270
can we meet and talk?

22:17.480 --> 22:20.480
From now on,
don't bother me with her matters anymore.

22:31.350 --> 22:31.880
Ms. Yan.

22:32.680 --> 22:33.740
Class is over, huh?

22:43.790 --> 22:44.200
Hello?

22:44.640 --> 22:45.040
Hello.

22:45.310 --> 22:46.440
Is that Ms. Yan Ling?

22:46.750 --> 22:47.480
Yes, speaking.

22:47.480 --> 22:47.930
Hello.

22:48.240 --> 22:49.460
I'm the legal counsel for Mr. Ding Zhibo

22:49.460 --> 22:51.860
and the Oceanvision International Group.

22:51.980 --> 22:54.240
[Oceanvision International Group]

22:52.510 --> 22:54.350
Given
Mr. Ding's current physical condition

22:54.350 --> 22:56.570
and his responsibility
to the Oceanvision International Group,

22:56.570 --> 22:57.590
he has voluntarily signed

22:57.590 --> 22:59.560
an authorization letter
for his medical care and treatment

22:59.560 --> 23:00.890
as well as a living will.

23:01.190 --> 23:02.750
And he requests you to be his

23:02.780 --> 23:04.020
authorized executor.

23:04.020 --> 23:04.960
A living will

23:04.150 --> 23:08.280
[Certificate of Honor]

23:05.070 --> 23:06.510
is signed when a person

23:06.510 --> 23:08.400
is healthy or conscious.

23:08.920 --> 23:09.480
Mr. Ding

23:09.640 --> 23:10.440
foresees that

23:10.550 --> 23:11.810
at the end of his life,

23:12.000 --> 23:13.110
he will inevitably face some

23:13.110 --> 23:14.490
major medical decisions,

23:14.490 --> 23:16.020
and he needs someone to sign

23:16.350 --> 23:17.950
the surgical consent forms.

23:18.350 --> 23:18.960
Yan Ling.

23:20.270 --> 23:21.110
As you know,

23:22.110 --> 23:23.720
my son died in an accident

23:24.440 --> 23:25.640
a long time ago,

23:26.310 --> 23:28.170
and I got divorced a few years ago.

23:29.550 --> 23:31.240
I have no relatives by my side.

23:32.150 --> 23:32.750
Mr. Ding.

23:33.440 --> 23:34.500
You have a company,

23:35.200 --> 23:36.070
lawyers,

23:36.160 --> 23:36.960
subordinates

23:37.440 --> 23:38.330
and friends.

23:38.750 --> 23:39.350
Ms. Yan.

23:40.510 --> 23:42.310
Mr. Ding's health or death

23:42.640 --> 23:44.770
has a significant impact on our group.

23:44.960 --> 23:47.030
Due to conflicts of interest,

23:47.350 --> 23:49.310
the top executives and partners
of our group,

23:49.310 --> 23:50.880
including our legal team,

23:51.310 --> 23:52.720
cannot become his authorized executor

23:52.720 --> 23:54.720
for his medical care and treatment.

23:56.680 --> 23:57.280
I'm sorry.

23:58.070 --> 23:59.400
I don't want to, either.

23:59.510 --> 24:00.160
I know

24:00.440 --> 24:02.070
this responsibility

24:02.110 --> 24:03.030
is very heavy for you.

24:03.030 --> 24:03.560
Alright.

24:06.350 --> 24:07.750
She and I will talk alone.

24:08.070 --> 24:08.550
Okay.

24:16.680 --> 24:17.940
Why are you doing this?

24:18.790 --> 24:21.120
You clearly know that I would never agree.

24:21.640 --> 24:24.110
But there's no one else I can trust.

24:25.720 --> 24:27.100
My business is so big

24:27.350 --> 24:29.210
that there will always be rivals.

24:29.310 --> 24:30.750
Who knows where they are hiding

24:30.750 --> 24:32.200
or who they have bribed?

24:34.310 --> 24:34.880
Ling.

24:35.790 --> 24:38.190
Now that
I'm on the verge of death like this,

24:38.750 --> 24:39.720
in this world,

24:39.720 --> 24:41.580
the only relatives I can trust now

24:42.790 --> 24:44.590
are you and your mom.

24:44.750 --> 24:46.080
Leave my mom out of this.

24:56.640 --> 24:57.310
I know

24:58.310 --> 25:00.540
you definitely don't love me

25:01.200 --> 25:01.920
as much as I love you.

25:01.920 --> 25:02.830
Stop saying it.

25:05.000 --> 25:05.530
Alright.

25:07.030 --> 25:07.920
You hate me.

25:09.480 --> 25:10.920
But so what?

25:12.480 --> 25:14.110
Since you were 14,

25:14.880 --> 25:16.830
regarding your studies, your life

25:16.830 --> 25:18.440
and how you've grown up to be an adult,

25:18.440 --> 25:20.900
I've been involved in every step,
haven't I?

25:29.030 --> 25:29.880
Ling.

25:31.030 --> 25:32.270
Now I'm giving my life

25:32.270 --> 25:33.590
to you.

25:35.920 --> 25:38.510
As long as you become
the authorized executor,

25:38.510 --> 25:41.310
you'll have the power
to decide on my life or death.

25:42.720 --> 25:43.480
When you allow me

25:43.480 --> 25:46.000
to undergo a very dangerous surgery,

25:46.000 --> 25:47.790
if I die on the operating table,

25:50.480 --> 25:52.680
wouldn't you laugh out loud
even in your dreams?

25:52.680 --> 25:53.440
Shut up!

25:56.720 --> 25:58.830
You clearly know
I'm not someone like that.

25:58.830 --> 25:59.630
That's right.

26:00.480 --> 26:02.510
I know you're not someone like that,

26:02.510 --> 26:03.830
so I trust you

26:03.830 --> 26:05.690
and dare to entrust my life to you.

26:08.720 --> 26:10.270
You don't actually trust me.

26:10.270 --> 26:12.000
You've signed this living will

26:12.790 --> 26:14.790
because you're just worried
that before you die,

26:14.790 --> 26:17.880
someone who hates you
would demand a tracheotomy and intubation,

26:17.880 --> 26:19.610
making your life a living hell.

26:23.000 --> 26:24.060
You little rascal.

26:26.030 --> 26:27.510
You're the smartest one.

26:32.070 --> 26:34.680
But I do need someone who can

26:35.000 --> 26:38.460
sign the surgical consent form for me
in a critical emergency.

26:42.880 --> 26:44.210
It's been so many years.

26:45.000 --> 26:47.060
I've never asked Ms. Su for anything.

26:48.160 --> 26:49.480
But whenever she asks,

26:49.480 --> 26:50.610
no matter what it is,

26:51.110 --> 26:53.000
I'd go through fire and water for her,

26:53.000 --> 26:56.060
including the 10 million yuan
I donated to your school.

26:56.680 --> 26:58.540
She has never known how to thank me

26:59.110 --> 27:00.160
or repay me.

27:01.070 --> 27:02.400
And I've always told her

27:03.640 --> 27:06.370
since we're a family,
there's no need to thank me.

27:06.550 --> 27:08.830
How about I go beg my good sister-in-law,

27:09.590 --> 27:10.270
or rather,

27:11.350 --> 27:12.350
my good sister?

27:13.680 --> 27:15.210
She will definitely agree.

27:16.270 --> 27:18.730
She has always been worried
about my health.

27:18.830 --> 27:19.830
What's more, she'll definitely

27:19.830 --> 27:21.720
discuss with you from time to time

27:22.110 --> 27:24.570
what kind of treatment plan
is better for me.

27:25.310 --> 27:26.510
She's not so ruthless

27:28.110 --> 27:29.440
as you are.

27:36.920 --> 27:38.710
Later, in our recital,

27:38.740 --> 27:40.680
don't make any mistakes
and don't be nervous.

27:40.680 --> 27:41.590
You can do it.

27:41.830 --> 27:42.440
Ms. Qiao,

27:42.720 --> 27:44.590
thank you
for giving the kids this opportunity.

27:44.590 --> 27:46.250
They are all extremely happy.

27:46.400 --> 27:47.600
Mr. Ding has said that

27:47.640 --> 27:49.240
children are the future of our country.

27:49.240 --> 27:49.590
Yes.

27:49.920 --> 27:51.520
So we must nurture them well.

28:31.900 --> 28:32.420
[Moments]

28:32.420 --> 28:34.940
[The scenery is beautiful,
and the environment is nice.]

28:34.960 --> 28:37.990
[The weather's nice. I'm playing
basketball with my colleagues.]

28:40.440 --> 28:41.230
[Walking out of the house
to embrace nature.]

28:41.250 --> 28:42.010
[Making every mountain hiking
a baptism of the soul.]

28:42.030 --> 28:42.710
[Mountain hiking
is not only a way of exercises,]

28:42.730 --> 28:43.490
[but it also enables us to talk to nature.
Let's enjoy every moment of life.]

28:43.510 --> 28:44.100
[As time goes by,
the passion in my heart still remains.]

28:44.130 --> 28:44.900
[Every step
is the pursuit for a good life.]

28:45.350 --> 28:48.680
Hearing a familiar melody by chance
on the streets of Gangdao,

28:48.680 --> 28:50.540
I can't help but think of the past.

28:51.680 --> 28:52.880
As soon as I heard this song

28:52.880 --> 28:55.680
from someone else's Moments,
I fell in love with it.

28:55.680 --> 28:57.270
Maybe I love it
because of the person who shared it.

28:56.300 --> 28:59.390
[Springtime for the Wild Lily]

28:58.750 --> 28:59.680
Unfortunately,

29:00.550 --> 29:01.690
to that person,

29:01.720 --> 29:03.720
all of this may have never happened.

29:03.920 --> 29:05.850
It's just my own wishful thinking.

29:07.480 --> 29:09.950
♪ It's like a dream ♪

29:10.800 --> 29:13.730
♪ Our encounter was so fleeting ♪

29:14.980 --> 29:16.430
♪ You came like a spring breeze ♪

29:16.700 --> 29:21.350
♪ Softly blowing into my heart ♪

29:22.280 --> 29:28.980
♪ Where has your smile gone? ♪

29:23.320 --> 29:23.830
[Hearing a familiar melody by chance
on the streets of Gangdao,]

29:23.860 --> 29:24.430
[I can't help but think of the past.
As soon as I heard this song]

29:24.450 --> 29:24.810
[from someone else's Moments,
I fell in love with it.]

29:24.840 --> 29:25.320
[Maybe I love it
because of the person who shared it.]

29:25.380 --> 29:28.040
[Dr. Luo Liang]

29:28.060 --> 29:30.060
[I just found out you went to Gangdao.]

29:29.830 --> 29:35.740
♪ That familiar smile I remember so well ♪

29:30.090 --> 29:32.860
[When you come back,
can we meet and talk?]

29:36.170 --> 29:40.880
♪ Do you know that I love you, miss you,
resent you, and long for you? ♪

29:41.130 --> 29:43.580
♪ My love will never change ♪

29:44.670 --> 29:48.340
♪ Have you ever thought about ♪

29:48.650 --> 29:51.460
♪ The vow we once made? ♪

29:52.150 --> 29:55.850
♪ Even if you're drawn to the daffodils ♪

29:56.130 --> 29:58.320
♪ Blooming by the water ♪

30:03.270 --> 30:04.200
Don't be afraid.

30:04.510 --> 30:05.170
Follow me.

30:15.270 --> 30:16.040
Who is it?

30:16.640 --> 30:17.270
It's me.

30:21.680 --> 30:22.410
Take the bag.

30:47.830 --> 30:48.750
Who is she?

30:52.440 --> 30:53.440
She's my sister.

30:54.880 --> 30:56.280
Don't you recognize her?

30:57.000 --> 30:57.750
Yuan?

30:59.110 --> 31:00.170
Are you saying that

31:01.510 --> 31:02.510
she's Yuan?

31:04.310 --> 31:07.110
Where did you
put my sister's clothes previously?

31:10.200 --> 31:10.830
Yuan.

31:20.110 --> 31:21.830
How could this be Yuan?

31:23.640 --> 31:25.680
You don't recognize her
just because of the burns?

31:25.680 --> 31:28.760
I'd recognize my girl
even if she had turned into ashes.

31:31.110 --> 31:32.350
Quit your job.

31:33.070 --> 31:34.400
I'll pay you the salary.

31:35.400 --> 31:38.000
My sister needs someone
to take care of her now.

31:38.830 --> 31:40.110
If she runs out again,

31:41.000 --> 31:42.930
we really won't be able to find her.

31:43.190 --> 31:44.450
Who is she exactly?

31:48.880 --> 31:49.480
I told you.

31:50.880 --> 31:51.810
She's my sister.

31:57.440 --> 31:59.790
Go boil some water and give her a bath.

32:16.170 --> 32:18.480
[Dongchuan Public Security Department]

32:16.310 --> 32:17.960
The CIC of our
Provincial Public Security Department

32:17.960 --> 32:20.680
worked with Lihai Public Security Bureau
and other relevant departments.

32:20.680 --> 32:22.600
After their continuous efforts
for several months,

32:21.070 --> 32:22.770
[Summary and Commendation Conference
for the 2/18 Special Operation]

32:22.720 --> 32:24.880
they've successfully sovled
the 2/18 Major New-Type Telecom Fraud Case

32:24.880 --> 32:26.400
under the supervision
of the Ministry of Public Security.

32:26.400 --> 32:27.460
Congratulations.

32:27.830 --> 32:29.310
The suspsects arrested by them included
the gang leaders, namely the He brothers.

32:29.310 --> 32:30.370
Congratulations.

32:30.960 --> 32:32.310
The executives, Lin

32:32.120 --> 32:37.260
[Summary and Commendation Conference
for the 2/18 Special Operation]

32:32.430 --> 32:34.640
and Ou, and so on.

32:34.680 --> 32:35.750
Ms. Wang Haoying.

32:35.960 --> 32:37.830
There were 277 bank cards,

32:38.110 --> 32:40.310
linking over 500 cases nationwide,

32:40.480 --> 32:42.590
with the involved amount
exceeding 160 million yuan.

32:42.590 --> 32:43.650
Congratulations.

32:45.440 --> 32:46.480
Mr. Li Feng.

32:52.750 --> 32:54.440
I was actually super nervous.

32:54.830 --> 32:56.850
My legs kept shaking just now.

32:57.000 --> 32:58.000
I saw it.

33:00.110 --> 33:03.170
So can I come back to find you again
after I return there?

33:08.440 --> 33:09.000
Well...

33:10.680 --> 33:13.540
I just feel that
this Mister, who Xia Yi mentioned,

33:15.000 --> 33:17.070
doesn't seem like a fabricated character.

33:17.070 --> 33:18.070
What do you think?

33:20.880 --> 33:23.080
I saw those website screenshots of his.

33:23.110 --> 33:24.400
Lin Huosheng is very cunning.

33:24.400 --> 33:26.240
Those are definitely fake screenshots.

33:26.240 --> 33:28.720
He was prepared to shift the blame
when things came to light.

33:28.720 --> 33:31.050
You know what?
I actually look down on him.

33:31.070 --> 33:33.400
He didn't even
graduate from the middle school,

33:33.400 --> 33:34.510
so how could he invent that...

33:33.480 --> 33:37.620
[Dongchuan Public Security Department]

33:35.680 --> 33:36.480
Hexagon.

33:36.960 --> 33:37.690
Hexagon.

33:37.720 --> 33:38.120
Right.

33:38.680 --> 33:40.400
See? Even I can't pronounce it.

33:40.400 --> 33:41.510
If he could invent that thing,

33:41.510 --> 33:42.270
I'd break my other arm

33:42.270 --> 33:43.270
and give it to him.

33:46.720 --> 33:48.190
Even if what he said was true,

33:48.190 --> 33:49.960
there's also nothing
we could do about him.

33:49.960 --> 33:51.270
The content he posted

33:51.270 --> 33:52.640
was shocking and eye-catching,

33:52.640 --> 33:54.790
but it doesn't count as
obscene information.

33:54.790 --> 33:57.270
At most, it shows
this Mister lacks moral integrity.

33:57.270 --> 33:58.920
Even the law can't control him.

33:58.920 --> 34:01.450
Besides,
that forum was closed down long ago.

34:02.510 --> 34:03.310
That's true.

34:05.920 --> 34:07.720
But what about
those girls who committed suicide

34:07.720 --> 34:09.719
in his White Mice Experiment Diary?

34:09.840 --> 34:10.969
I've read that, too.

34:11.510 --> 34:13.320
There's no evidence to verify the content.

34:13.320 --> 34:14.920
Even if that Mister was real,

34:15.440 --> 34:16.710
and even if we could find him,

34:16.710 --> 34:17.630
he could simply say that

34:17.630 --> 34:19.000
it was just a novel he wrote.

34:19.000 --> 34:21.330
You wouldn't have any way
to deal with him.

34:22.190 --> 34:23.070
Officer Li.

34:23.300 --> 34:25.540
[Police]

34:23.670 --> 34:24.320
Chief Hu.

34:24.590 --> 34:25.440
Master!

34:25.670 --> 34:28.159
[Police]

34:25.710 --> 34:28.639
Today, I'm acting as a driver
for our one-armed hero.

34:29.150 --> 34:31.210
I can even get this kind of treatment?

34:33.070 --> 34:34.199
I'll get going then.

34:34.949 --> 34:37.389
[Police]

34:36.840 --> 34:37.570
Yes, you can.

34:38.550 --> 34:39.480
What do you mean?

34:39.710 --> 34:41.179
If you have any matters in the future,

34:41.179 --> 34:42.780
you can come find me anytime.

34:44.760 --> 34:45.230
Okay.

34:47.670 --> 34:48.440
Second-Class Merit, Master.

34:48.440 --> 34:49.760
-Keep working hard.
-Second-Class Merit.

34:49.760 --> 34:50.360
Alright.

34:50.360 --> 34:51.360
With this, I'll meet the requirements
for joining the Party, right?

34:51.360 --> 34:52.420
Just get in the car.

35:03.840 --> 35:06.170
The Paw Patrol made a great contribution.

35:10.150 --> 35:13.210
[Lihai Mingde International Hospital]

35:11.760 --> 35:13.190
I've told you guys that

35:13.800 --> 35:14.630
in this kind of situation,

35:14.630 --> 35:16.840
there's absolutely no need
to bother Ms. Yan.

35:16.840 --> 35:17.670
Look at you guys.

35:17.670 --> 35:19.130
You are really something.

35:19.380 --> 35:22.080
Mr. Ding,
I completely understand how you feel.

35:20.180 --> 35:26.250
[Lihai Mingde International Hospital]

35:22.580 --> 35:24.620
But the recent test results

35:24.930 --> 35:26.190
are all very worrying.

35:26.500 --> 35:28.090
Given your current physical condition,

35:28.090 --> 35:30.760
we do not recommend
that you go on a long trip.

35:31.320 --> 35:33.520
For such a severely ill patient like me,

35:33.800 --> 35:35.980
it'd be weird if the results were normal.

35:35.980 --> 35:37.040
Do I have to stay in the hospital
all this time

35:37.040 --> 35:38.640
until I die?

35:39.170 --> 35:42.530
[Lihai Mingde International Hospital]

35:39.630 --> 35:41.890
I'm going to Dubai
to look into a new drug.

35:42.230 --> 35:44.830
It might be more effective
than all your drugs.

35:48.030 --> 35:49.230
I'm sorry, Ms. Yan,

35:49.670 --> 35:51.730
for suddenly asking you to come here.

35:51.800 --> 35:55.340
You're the authorized executor
for Mr. Ding's medical care and treatment.

35:55.340 --> 35:58.450
To be honest, we don't often encounter
this kind of situation,

35:58.450 --> 35:59.780
so we are very cautious.

36:00.560 --> 36:01.770
Mr. Ding insists on

36:01.800 --> 36:03.590
leaving the hospital to travel.

36:03.590 --> 36:05.280
After our repeated consideration,

36:05.280 --> 36:07.710
we've decided
that both you and Mr. Ding must sign.

36:07.710 --> 36:10.040
In case that anything unexpected happens

36:10.320 --> 36:12.630
while Mr. Ding is traveling,

36:12.850 --> 36:14.250
even if he doesn't sue us,

36:14.350 --> 36:16.350
you'll still have the right to do so.

36:16.760 --> 36:17.960
-I won't.
-She won't.

36:19.290 --> 36:21.810
[Lihai Mingde International Hospital]

36:25.070 --> 36:27.030
Mr. Ding is fully conscious now.

36:27.650 --> 36:28.780
I think he's

36:28.810 --> 36:31.740
completely capable of
taking responsibility for his actions.

36:31.740 --> 36:33.940
As his so-called authorized executor,

36:34.190 --> 36:36.450
I also have to respect Mr. Ding's wishes.

36:37.920 --> 36:39.180
See what I've told you?

36:39.510 --> 36:40.030
Right?

36:42.000 --> 36:44.400
There's no need
to vent your anger all on me.

36:44.590 --> 36:46.400
I told them not to bother you,

36:46.400 --> 36:48.550
but they insisted on asking you to sign.
So...

36:48.550 --> 36:50.920
This authorization of yours
is unnecessary anyway.

36:50.920 --> 36:51.880
Well, don't worry, Yan Ling.

36:51.880 --> 36:53.320
If I really need surgery,

36:53.320 --> 36:54.070
you'll need to sign.

36:54.070 --> 36:55.440
But other than that,
you usually don't need to worry about me.

36:55.440 --> 36:56.770
I won't worry about you.

36:57.320 --> 36:58.180
Hello, Ms. Yan.

36:58.190 --> 36:58.880
The car has been arranged.

36:58.880 --> 36:59.670
We can head straight to the airport.

36:59.670 --> 37:00.400
Please go in.

37:03.590 --> 37:06.350
Ms. Chen, aren't you going with us?

37:06.670 --> 37:08.200
Going abroad is expensive.

37:08.440 --> 37:08.880
This time, you two

37:08.880 --> 37:12.320
are going abroad for a competition,
and it costs a lot of money.

37:12.320 --> 37:13.510
With Ms. Qiao accompanying you two,

37:13.510 --> 37:14.670
just do your best in the competition

37:14.670 --> 37:16.470
and try to bring back a big prize.

37:19.670 --> 37:20.730
Hello, Uncle Ding.

37:20.760 --> 37:21.400
Hello.

37:21.400 --> 37:22.150
Just get in the car.

37:22.150 --> 37:22.440
Thank you, Mr. Ding.

37:22.440 --> 37:23.480
Otherwise, you'll miss your flight.

37:23.480 --> 37:24.960
Don't worry.
Someone will take good care of them.

37:24.960 --> 37:25.490
Alright.

37:25.920 --> 37:27.760
You two must listen to Uncle Ding.

37:27.760 --> 37:28.230
Okay.

37:28.230 --> 37:28.900
Just go.

37:29.000 --> 37:29.710
Goodbye, Ms. Chen.

37:29.710 --> 37:30.170
Bye bye.

37:30.190 --> 37:31.190
Bye bye, Ms. Chen.

37:31.190 --> 37:32.250
-Bye bye.
-Bye bye.

37:32.320 --> 37:32.880
Good luck.

37:32.880 --> 37:33.230
Okay.

37:33.230 --> 37:33.800
Bye bye.

37:33.820 --> 37:34.280
Bye bye.

37:37.070 --> 37:39.280
I'm counting on you
to take Ling to school.

37:39.280 --> 37:40.080
Get in the car.

37:40.630 --> 37:41.000
Come.

37:44.190 --> 37:44.670
Come on.

37:44.990 --> 37:46.110
Now that you're a student
in a top provincial school,

37:46.110 --> 37:47.440
you need to study hard

37:47.590 --> 37:48.990
and listen to Uncle Ding.

37:55.510 --> 37:57.630
Stop the car!

37:59.360 --> 38:01.130
Stop the car!

38:01.920 --> 38:03.840
Stop the car. Get out of the car now.

38:03.840 --> 38:05.000
Hurry up. Take your things.

38:05.000 --> 38:05.710
Go home at once.

38:05.710 --> 38:06.440
You can't go.

38:06.440 --> 38:07.090
Who are you?

38:07.090 --> 38:07.840
Come on.

38:07.880 --> 38:08.670
Call your parents.

38:08.670 --> 38:09.590
Who are you?

38:09.590 --> 38:10.630
You can't let them go.

38:10.630 --> 38:11.880
What are you doing, Yan Ling?

38:11.880 --> 38:13.080
You can't let them go.

38:13.110 --> 38:14.400
You absolutely can't let them go.

38:14.400 --> 38:15.230
Go home at once.

38:15.230 --> 38:15.920
Yan Ling!

38:15.920 --> 38:16.840
Let go!

38:16.840 --> 38:17.670
What are you doing?

38:17.670 --> 38:18.570
Trust me, Ma'am.

38:18.570 --> 38:19.440
Take your hands off them!

38:19.440 --> 38:20.880
What does this have to do with you?

38:20.880 --> 38:22.440
-You can't let them go.
-They're going to the competition, okay?

38:22.440 --> 38:23.360
Don't let them go.

38:23.360 --> 38:23.840
Take the kids into the car!

38:23.840 --> 38:24.630
Don't let them go!

38:24.630 --> 38:25.590
You can't let them go!

38:25.590 --> 38:27.590
-Let go!
-Take the kids into the car!

38:27.800 --> 38:28.760
Don't let them leave!

38:28.760 --> 38:29.400
You can't get in the car!

38:29.400 --> 38:30.150
Don't do that!

38:30.150 --> 38:31.030
Hurry! Get in the car!

38:31.030 --> 38:31.960
I'm begging you!

38:32.070 --> 38:33.470
You can't let the kids go!

38:33.630 --> 38:34.630
Don't let them go!

38:34.840 --> 38:36.440
I can't let you do the same thing

38:36.440 --> 38:38.440
to them as you did to me back then!

38:38.440 --> 38:40.280
Let go of me!

38:40.840 --> 38:42.770
Get out of the car! You can't leave!

38:43.320 --> 38:44.520
Get out of the car now!

38:47.480 --> 38:49.280
Ma'am, tell them to get out of the car.

38:49.280 --> 38:49.840
They can't go!

38:49.840 --> 38:50.480
They can't go!

38:50.480 --> 38:51.400
Drive!

38:51.670 --> 38:52.230
You can't go.

38:52.230 --> 38:53.630
Get out of the car now. Okay?

38:53.630 --> 38:55.150
It's not safe for the kids.

38:55.150 --> 38:55.670
Let go!

38:55.670 --> 38:56.770
I'm begging you.

38:57.070 --> 38:57.800
Let go first.

38:57.960 --> 39:00.110
Ask them to get out of the car!

39:00.400 --> 39:01.250
Go, go, go!

39:01.360 --> 39:02.480
Don't go!

39:04.880 --> 39:06.230
Don't go!

39:08.630 --> 39:09.920
Come back!

39:10.960 --> 39:12.110
Come back!

39:13.000 --> 39:14.440
You can't go!

39:15.480 --> 39:16.310
No!

39:16.360 --> 39:18.550
Don't drive! Come back!

39:19.030 --> 39:20.110
Come back!

39:29.510 --> 39:31.070
-You can't let them go.
-They're going to the competition, okay?

39:31.070 --> 39:32.550
Don't let them go!

39:36.550 --> 39:37.920
Don't let them go!

39:38.110 --> 39:38.670
Get in the car!

39:38.670 --> 39:39.600
I'm begging you!

39:39.920 --> 39:41.320
You can't let the kids go!

39:41.840 --> 39:43.480
I can't let you do the same thing

39:43.480 --> 39:45.360
to them as you did to me back then!

39:45.360 --> 39:46.070
Let go of me!

39:46.280 --> 39:46.940
Let go of me!

39:47.920 --> 39:48.920
Get out of the car!

39:49.930 --> 39:50.540
[The Chairman
of Oceanvision International Group]

39:50.560 --> 39:51.480
[Is suspected
to sexually assault an underage girl!]

39:51.500 --> 39:52.880
[A college professor revealed
her painful past in public!]

40:00.070 --> 40:01.000
It's time to eat.

40:25.190 --> 40:27.590
I'll book a ticket to go back
after the meal.

40:28.890 --> 40:31.830
Didn't you say
you'd stay a couple more days?

40:32.590 --> 40:33.850
I have something to do.

40:35.150 --> 40:35.610
Then...

40:36.280 --> 40:38.940
I'll stir-fry some celtuce for you.
You love it.

40:59.230 --> 41:00.360
What's wrong?

41:01.840 --> 41:02.920
Fire, fire, fire!

41:02.920 --> 41:04.110
Turn it off!

41:04.230 --> 41:05.000
Fire, fire!

41:05.920 --> 41:06.980
I've turned it off.

41:07.030 --> 41:08.070
The fire is gone now.

41:08.070 --> 41:08.860
Fire, fire!

41:09.000 --> 41:10.150
The fire is gone now! It's gone!

41:10.150 --> 41:11.550
Stand up!

41:11.960 --> 41:12.800
Mom!

41:14.400 --> 41:15.710
Mom!

41:16.550 --> 41:17.330
Mom's here.

41:17.800 --> 41:18.500
Mom's here.

41:28.850 --> 41:30.050
Take good care of her.

41:30.610 --> 41:32.270
I'll pack my things and leave.

41:43.680 --> 41:44.360
Mom.

41:48.550 --> 41:49.440
Mom's here.

41:50.590 --> 41:51.320
Mom.

41:54.550 --> 41:59.060
[The Dark Romance]

42:01.770 --> 42:07.100
[2013]

42:07.540 --> 42:08.730
[Amusement Park: Emotion Sharing Forum]

42:08.730 --> 42:09.730
[Experiment Diary]

42:08.850 --> 42:10.620
Exclusive Tattoo and Mark.

42:09.780 --> 42:10.910
[White Mice Experiment 18:
Exclusive Tattoo and Mark]

42:12.790 --> 42:13.060
[Amusement Park: Emotion Sharing Forum]

42:17.660 --> 42:18.520
[Li Ming asked Xiaoyu to get a tattoo.
Superficially, this action]

42:18.550 --> 42:19.520
[seemed to show care and encouragement.
But deep down in his heart,]

42:19.550 --> 42:20.140
[this was actually a game.]

42:20.160 --> 42:20.740
[Through this action,
he wanted to force Xiaoyu]

42:20.760 --> 42:21.750
[to prove her love and attention to him.]

42:27.490 --> 42:30.120
This guy is a genius.

42:30.170 --> 42:31.050
[White Mice Experiment: Snow Queen]

42:31.070 --> 42:32.750
[The Power of Influence]

42:32.770 --> 42:33.430
[Love Experiment 9:
Share Secrets to Get Closer]

42:33.450 --> 42:34.650
[Feedback of Pet Raising Techniques]

42:33.960 --> 42:34.680
Web Administrator!

42:34.680 --> 42:37.340
[Mister]

42:35.150 --> 42:36.110
Give me one more bottle of beer!
